---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="School Age Programs">
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface-sand relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white border border-brand-sky/30 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-sky uppercase tracking-wide mb-6">
        Ages K5 - 6th Grade
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">School Age Programs</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-slate max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Before and after school care that balances homework support with social development and fun.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-brand-navy max-w-none text-text-ink leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Milestones' School Age program is designed with the unique needs of older children in mind. Operating out of our Lydell Community Center and Indian Hill School locations, we provide a structured yet flexible environment where students can thrive outside of regular school hours.
        </p>

        <h2>Before & After School</h2>
        <p>
          Mornings start calmly, allowing children to prepare for the school day ahead. In the afternoons, children can unwind, participate in recreational activities, and get a head start on their homework. 
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-surface-sand p-6 rounded-2xl border border-surface-mist">
            <h3 class="mt-0 pt-0 text-xl">Homework Support</h3>
            <p class="text-base mb-0">Our staff is available to assist students with their assignments, providing a quiet space and the guidance needed to foster good study habits.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-sand p-6 rounded-2xl border border-surface-mist">
            <h3 class="mt-0 pt-0 text-xl">Social Development</h3>
            <p class="text-base mb-0">We emphasize character building, cooperation, and conflict resolution through team games and community projects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Schools We Serve</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Atwater School</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Lake Bluff School</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Holy Family School</strong> (also serving Cumberland students)</li>
          <li><strong>Indian Hill School</strong> (also serving Maple Dale students)</li>
          <li><strong>Parkway School</strong> (also serving Glen Hills students)</li>
          <li><strong>St. Monica School</strong> (also serving Richards students)</li>
          <li><strong>St. Robert School</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <a href="/parents/enrollment" class="btn-primary no-underline text-white inline-flex">Enroll Your Child</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
